   "source": [
    "# Chapter 7 Formula Sheet\n",
    "\n",
    "## n-step Return\n",
    "$$\n",
    "G_{t:t+n} = R_{t+1} + \\cdots + \\gamma^{n-1}R_{t+n} + \\gamma^n V(S_{t+n})\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "## n-step TD update\n",
    "$$\n",
    "V(S_t) \\leftarrow V(S_t) + \\alpha [G_{t:t+n} - V(S_t)]\n",
    "$$\n"
   ]
  }
